  "Description": {
    "English": "This sculptural piece is a result of the anomalous geology on some superheated worlds. Molten lava burst forth from beneath the ground and then congealed rapidly, preserving what would otherwise be a moment of ephemeral beauty.<br><br>Provides decorative landscaping opportunities for bases.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这件雕塑作品源自某些过热星球的异常地质。熔岩从地下喷涌而出，而后又迅速凝结，将原本转瞬即逝的美景保留了下来。<br><br>可以作为基地的装饰景观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這件雕塑作品取自某些高熱星球的異常地質構造。岩漿從地下噴湧而出，然後迅速凝結，保留了原本轉瞬即逝的自然之美。<br><br>可為基地提供景觀美化的機會。"
  },
